  <summary>3/16/1988--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code with respect to the excise tax on diesel and aviation fuels. Prohibits imposition of the tax on the sale of these fuels to any purchaser (or purchaser for resale to a second purchaser) for use: (1) on a farm for farming purposes; or (2) in a vessel in commercial waterway transportation.</summary>
